        exercise: "Complete this beginner bodyweight circuit three times this week with at least one rest day between sessions: 10 wall push-ups, 10 chair-assisted squats, 20-second knee plank, 10 standing calf raises, 10 step-ups on a sturdy step. Rest 60 seconds between exercises. Record how many reps you completed and how you felt. Aim to add 2 reps or 5 seconds to each exercise weekly.",
